## ğŸ¨ DESIGN SYSTEM & COLOR PALETTE

### PRIMARY COLORS

```
#1a1a2e  - Dark Background (Primary)
#16213e  - Dark Background (Secondary)
#0f3460  - Accent (Darker Blue)
#00d4ff  - Primary Action (Cyan) â† Brand Color
#00a8cc  - Primary Hover (Darker Cyan)
#00ff88  - Success (Bright Green)
#ffaa00  - Warning (Orange)
#ff3344  - Error (Red)
#ffffff  - Text Primary
#cccccc  - Text Secondary
#666666  - Text Tertiary
```

### SEMANTIC COLORS

```
Success:   #00ff88 (RGB: 0, 255, 136)
Warning:   #ffaa00 (RGB: 255, 170, 0)
Error:     #ff3344 (RGB: 255, 51, 68)
Info:      #00d4ff (RGB: 0, 212, 255)
Running:   #00ff88 (Green - Active)
Stopped:   #666666 (Gray - Inactive)
Error Sta: #ff3344 (Red - Failed)
Pending:   #ffaa00 (Orange - Processing)
```

### GRADIENTS

```
Primary Gradient:
  from: #0f3460
  to: #1a1a2e

Success Gradient:
  from: #00ff88
  to: #00cc66

Error Gradient:
  from: #ff3344
  to: #cc0022
```

