## ğŸ“‹ REGISTER PAGE

**URL:** `/register`  
**Layout:** IdentickÃ½ s Login (400px max)
**RozdÃ­ly:** VÃ­ce input polÃ­, dodateÄnÃ© validace

### FORM FIELDS

1. **Username**
   - Type: text
   - Placeholder: "3-32 znakÅ¯, alfanumerickÃ©"
   - Validation: regex `^[a-zA-Z0-9_]{3,32}$`
   - Help text: "3-32 znakÅ¯, pÃ­smena, ÄÃ­sla a _"

2. **Email**
   - Type: email
   - Placeholder: "vase@email.com"
   - Validation: RFC 5322 email
   - Help text: "Aktivujte ÃºÄet potvrzenÃ­m emailu"

3. **Password**
   - Type: password
   - Placeholder: "MinimÃ¡lnÄ› 8 znakÅ¯"
   - Validation: Min 8, 1 uppercase, 1 digit, 1 special
   - Strength indicator (visual bar):
     ```css
     .strength-bar {
       height: 4px;
       background: #333;
       border-radius: 2px;
       margin-top: 4px;
       overflow: hidden;
       
       .strength-fill {
         height: 100%;
         transition: width 250ms, background 250ms;
       }
       
       &.weak .strength-fill {
         width: 25%;
         background: #ff3344;
       }
       
       &.fair .strength-fill {
         width: 50%;
         background: #ffaa00;
       }
       
       &.good .strength-fill {
         width: 75%;
         background: #ffff00;
       }
       
       &.strong .strength-fill {
         width: 100%;
         background: #00ff88;
       }
     }
     ```
   - Help text: DynamickÃ½ - "PÅ™Ã­liÅ¡ slabÃ©" â†’ "SilnÃ© heslo"

4. **Confirm Password**
   - Type: password
   - Placeholder: "Zopakujte heslo"
   - Validation: MusÃ­ se shodovat s Password
   - Chyba pokud se neshoduje: "Hesla se neshodujÃ­"

5. **Terms & Conditions**
   - Type: checkbox
   - Text: "SouhlasÃ­m s [PodmÃ­nkami sluÅ¾by] a [ZÃ¡sadami ochrany"
   - PovinnÃ½: ANO
   - Chyba: "MusÃ­te souhlasit s podmÃ­nkami"

### VALIDATION FEEDBACK

```css
.input-wrapper {
  position: relative;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  
  .validation-icon {
    position: absolute;
    right: 12px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    font-size: 18px;
    
    &.success::before {
      content: "âœ“";
      color: #00ff88;
    }
    
    &.error::before {
      content: "âœ—";
      color: #ff3344;
    }
  }
}

.help-text {
  font-size: 12px;
  color: #999;
  margin-top: 4px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 4px;
  
  &.error {
    color: #ff3344;
  }
  
  &.success {
    color: #00ff88;
  }
}
```

