**Elements:**
- Hamburger menu (mobile only): 24x24px
- Logo + Text: "LONGIN" (16px, bold)
- Search input: Min 200px, placeholder: "Hledat aplikace..."
- Notification bell: Icon, red dot pokud pending (3px, #ff3344)
- User avatar: 32x32px, circular, initials/gravatar
- User dropdown: Username, Logout, Settings
- Settings icon: Gear icon, link to settings

### SIDEBAR (Collapsible)

**Desktop:** Always visible (width: 250px)  
**Tablet:** Hamburger toggle  
**Mobile:** Drawer over content

