**Tab Navigation:**
```css
.tab-nav {
  display: flex;
  border-bottom: 1px solid #0f3460;
  gap: 0;
  
  .tab {
    padding: 16px 24px;
    border: none;
    background: transparent;
    color: #999;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 250ms ease;
    position: relative;
    
    &:hover {
      color: #cccccc;
    }
    
    &.active {
      color: #00d4ff;
      
      &::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        bottom: -1px;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        height: 2px;
        background: #00d4ff;
      }
    }
  }
}
