## ğŸ§© KOMPONENTY - REUSABLE COMPONENTS

### BUTTON VARIANTS

```css
/* Primary Button */
.btn-primary {
  background: #00d4ff;
  color: #1a1a2e;
  padding: 12px 24px;
  
  &:hover { background: #00a8cc; }
}

/* Secondary Button */
.btn-secondary {
  background: transparent;
  color: #00d4ff;
  border: 1px solid #00d4ff;
  
  &:hover { background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1); }
}

/* Danger Button */
.btn-danger {
  background: #ff3344;
  color: #ffffff;
  
  &:hover { background: #cc0022; }
}

/* Success Button */
.btn-success {
  background: #00ff88;
  color: #1a1a2e;
  
  &:hover { background: #00cc66; }
}
```

### BADGE COMPONENTS

```css
.badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 6px;
  padding: 4px 12px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 600;
}

.badge-success {
  background: rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.15);
  color: #00ff88;
}

.badge-error {
  background: rgba(255, 51, 68, 0.15);
  color: #ff3344;
}

.badge-warning {
  background: rgba(255, 170, 0, 0.15);
  color: #ffaa00;
}

.badge-info {
  background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.15);
  color: #00d4ff;
}
```

### CARD COMPONENT

```css
.card {
  background: #16213e;
  border: 1px solid #0f3460;
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 20px;
  transition: all 250ms ease;
  
  &:hover {
    border-color: #00d4ff;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
  }
}
```

